rañjanādityanurāgaṇāt | prajñayā hyāśayānuśayaṃ vijñāya yathāyogamanuṣṭhānātsarvasattvā anurāgitā bhavantīti prajñaiva tathocyate |

<commentary>guṇasya balavaiśāradyādirūpasyākāśadhenordu-hanādutpādanātprajñaiva tathocyate | yathoktam—

	guṇāste 'paryantā yugapadabhisambodhisamaye 
	kuto 'pi tvāṃ prāptāstarumiva nivāsāya vihagāḥ || 

iti | cañcalatvāditi bhavanirvāṇāpratiṣṭhitatvena kutracidapratiṣṭhitatvāt | asparśeti śūnyataikarasatvāt |
bāhyānāmapi mudrāṇāmeteṣāmeva prajñāguṇānāmanukaraṇātprajñātvamanugantavyam | bāhyānāmeva prajñātvapratipādanārthamayaṃ grantha ityapare |</commentary>

utpannarūpāddevatāṃ pratipādya mantraṃ pratipādayannāha—jalpanamityādi |
